// Devoid = a characteristic-defining ability ([CR#604.3]): "this object is
// colorless", functioning in every zone. An empty color set IS colorless
// ([CR#105.2c]-style), so the CDA static sets colors to none. Mirrors
// Changeling's CDA shape (a `cda: true` static modifying `Of(This)`); the
// layer engine reads it at layer 5 (color-setting).
KeywordAbility(
    name: "Devoid",
    template: "devoid",
    abilities: [Static(
        cda: true,
        effects: [Modify(of: Of(This), changes: [Colors(Set([]))])],
    )],
)
